</ul></div></nav></div></header><div class="site-inner"><div class="wrap"><header class="entry-header" id="page-title"><h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Faculty Research</h1>
</header><div class="content-sidebar-wrap"><main class="content" id="genesis-content"><article class="post-10427 page type-page status-publish entry" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" itemref="page-title"><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text">
<p>Faculty in the Democratic Erosion Consortium have produced a wealth of research on the causes, symptoms and consequences of democratic erosion around the world. Find a selection of their work below.</p>



<div class="wp-block-columns has-2-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
