<p><strong>Tuncel, Jennifer McCoy, Benjamin Press, Murat Somer, Ozlem. </strong>“Reducing Pernicious Polarization: A Comparative Historical Analysis of Depolarization.” <em>Carnegie Endowment for International Peace</em>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-button btn-small"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://carnegieendowment.org/2022/05/05/reducing-pernicious-polarization-comparative-historical-analysis-of-depolarization-pub-87034" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read More</a></div>



